<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Thank You for Your Donation!</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
        .container { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        h1 { color: #111; font-size: 24px; text-align: center; }
        .amount-box { background: #f0f4f8; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
        .amount { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: #4f46e5; }
        .ref { margin-top: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #666; font-style: italic; }
        p { line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 40px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Thank you, <%= name %>!</h1>
        <p>Your generous donation helps us provide shelter, food, and medical care to dogs in need. We truly appreciate your support!</p>
        
        <div class="amount-box">
            <div class="amount"><%= currency %> <%= amount %></div>
            <% if (reference && reference !== 'None provided') { %>
                <div class="ref">Reference: <%= reference %></div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <p>Best regards,<br>The Calvoro Team</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> CALVORO. All Rights Reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
